text: Jerrybuccinum is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Species== Species within the genus Jerrybuccinum include: * Jerrybuccinum malvinense Kantor & Pastorino, 2009 * Jerrybuccinum explorator (Fraussen & Sellanes, 2008) ==References== Category:Buccinidae Category:Monotypic gastropod genera
title: Jerrybuccinum
